502  /* create residual history vector */
503  if( solver->residual ) lis_free(solver->residual);
504  residual = (LIS_SCALAR *)lis_malloc((maxiter+2)*sizeof(LIS_SCALAR),"lis_solve::residual");
505  if( residual==NULL )
506  {
507  LIS_SETERR_MEM((maxiter+2)*sizeof(LIS_SCALAR));
508  lis_vector_destroy(xx);
509  solver->retcode = err;
510  return err;
511  }
512  residual[0] = 1.0;
513 
514 
515  n = A->n;
516  np = A->np;
517  t = NULL;
518  At = NULL;
519 
520 
521  p_c_times = lis_wtime();
522  if( precon_type==LIS_PRECON_TYPE_IS )
523  {
524  if( solver->d==NULL )
525  {
526  err = lis_vector_duplicate(A,&solver->d);
527  if( err )
528  {
529  return err;
530  }
531  }
532  if( !A->is_scaled )
533  {
534  lis_matrix_scaling(A,b,solver->d,LIS_SCALE_JACOBI);
535  }
536  else if( !b->is_scaled )
537  {
538  #ifdef _OPENMP
539  #pragma omp parallel for
540  #endif
541  for(i=0;i<n;i++)
542  {
543  b->value[i] = b->value[i]*solver->d->value[i];
544  }
545  }
546  if( nsolver >= LIS_SOLVER_JACOBI && nsolver <= LIS_SOLVER_SOR )
547  {
548  solver->options[LIS_OPTIONS_ISLEVEL] = 0;
549  }
550  }
551  else if( nsolver >= LIS_SOLVER_JACOBI && nsolver <= LIS_SOLVER_SOR && precon_type!=LIS_PRECON_TYPE_NONE )
552  {
553  if( solver->d==NULL )
554  {
555  err = lis_vector_duplicate(A,&solver->d);
556  if( err )
557  {
558  return err;
559  }
560  }
561  if( !A->is_scaled )
562  {
563  lis_matrix_scaling(A,b,solver->d,LIS_SCALE_JACOBI);
564  }
565  }
566  else if( scale )
567  {
568  if( storage==LIS_MATRIX_BSR && scale==LIS_SCALE_JACOBI )
569  {
570  if( A->matrix_type!=LIS_MATRIX_BSR )
571  {
572  err = lis_matrix_duplicate(A,&B);
573  if( err ) return err;
574  lis_matrix_set_blocksize(B,block,block,NULL,NULL);
575  lis_matrix_set_type(B,storage);
576  err = lis_matrix_convert(A,B);
577  if( err ) return err;
578  lis_matrix_storage_destroy(A);
579  lis_matrix_DLU_destroy(A);
580  lis_matrix_diag_destroy(A->WD);
581  if( A->l2g_map ) lis_free( A->l2g_map );
582  if( A->commtable ) lis_commtable_destroy( A->commtable );
583  if( A->ranges ) lis_free( A->ranges );
584  err = lis_matrix_copy_struct(B,A);
585  if( err ) return err;
586  lis_free(B);
587  }
588  err = lis_matrix_split(A);
589  if( err ) return err;
590  err = lis_matrix_diag_duplicate(A->D,&solver->WD);
591  if( err ) return err;
592  lis_matrix_diag_copy(A->D,solver->WD);
593  lis_matrix_diag_inverse(solver->WD);
594  lis_matrix_bscaling_bsr(A,solver->WD);
595  lis_vector_duplicate(A,&t);
596  lis_matrix_diag_matvec(solver->WD,b,t);
597  lis_vector_copy(t,b);
598  lis_vector_destroy(t);
599  t = NULL;
600  }
601  else
602  {
603  if( solver->d==NULL )
604  {
605  err = lis_vector_duplicate(A,&solver->d);
606  if( err )
607  {
608  return err;
609  }
610  }
611  if( scale==LIS_SCALE_JACOBI && nsolver==LIS_SOLVER_CG )
612  {
613  scale = LIS_SCALE_SYMM_DIAG;
614  }
615  if( !A->is_scaled )
616  {
617  lis_matrix_scaling(A,b,solver->d,scale);
618  }
619  else if( !b->is_scaled )
620  {
621  #ifdef _OPENMP
622  #pragma omp parallel for
623  #endif
624  for(i=0;i<n;i++)
625  {
626  b->value[i] = b->value[i]*solver->d->value[i];
627  }
628  }
629  }
630  }
631 
632 /* precon_type = precon->precon_type;*/
633  if( precon_type==LIS_PRECON_TYPE_IS )
634  {
635  if( nsolver < LIS_SOLVER_JACOBI || nsolver > LIS_SOLVER_SOR )
636  {
637  AA = solver->A;
638  bb = solver->b;
639  }
640  else
641  {
642  AA = precon->A;
643  bb = precon->Pb;
644  }
645  }
646  else
647  {
648  AA = A;
649  bb = b;
650  }
651 
652  p_c_times = lis_wtime() - p_c_times;
653  itimes = lis_wtime();
654 
655  /* Matrix Convert */
656  solver->A = AA;
657  solver->b = bb;
658  err = lis_matrix_convert_self(solver);
659  if( err )
660  {
661  lis_vector_destroy(xx);
662  lis_solver_work_destroy(solver);
663  lis_free(residual);
664  solver->retcode = err;
665  return err;
666  }
667  block = solver->A->bnr;
668 
669  if( A->my_rank==0 )
670  {
671 #ifdef _LONG__DOUBLE
672  if( output ) printf("precision : long double\n");
673 #else
674  if( output ) printf("precision : %s\n", lis_precisionname[precision]);
675 #endif
676 #ifdef _LONGLONG
677  if( output ) printf("solver : %s %lld\n", lis_solvername[nsolver],nsolver);
678 #else
679  if( output ) printf("solver : %s %d\n", lis_solvername[nsolver],nsolver);
680 #endif
681  switch( precon_type )
682  {
683  case LIS_PRECON_TYPE_ILU:
684  i = solver->options[LIS_OPTIONS_FILL];
685  if( A->matrix_type==LIS_MATRIX_BSR || A->matrix_type==LIS_MATRIX_VBR )
686  {
687 #ifdef _LONGLONG
688  if( output ) sprintf(buf,"Block %s(%lld)",lis_preconname[precon_type],i);
689 #else
690  if( output ) sprintf(buf,"Block %s(%d)",lis_preconname[precon_type],i);
691 #endif
692  }
693  else
694  {
695 #ifdef _LONGLONG
696  if( output ) sprintf(buf,"%s(%lld)",lis_preconname[precon_type],i);
697 #else
698  if( output ) sprintf(buf,"%s(%d)",lis_preconname[precon_type],i);
699 #endif
700  }
701  break;
702  default:
703  if( output ) sprintf(buf,"%s",lis_preconname[precon_type]);
704  break;
705  }
706  if( solver->options[LIS_OPTIONS_ADDS] && precon_type )
707  {
708  if( output ) printf("precon : %s + additive schwarz\n", buf);
709  }
710  else
711  {
712  if( output ) printf("precon : %s\n", buf);
713  }
714  }
715  switch(conv_cond)
716  {
717  case LIS_CONV_COND_NRM2_R:
718  case LIS_CONV_COND_NRM2_B:
719  if( A->my_rank==0 )
720  {
721  if( output ) ("CONV_COND : ||r||_2 <= %6.1e*||r_0||_2\n", tol);
722  }
723  break;
724  case LIS_CONV_COND_NRM1_B:
725  lis_vector_nrm1(b,&nrm2);
726  nrm2 = nrm2*tol_w + tol;
727  if( A->my_rank==0 )
728  {
729  if( output ) printf("conv_cond : ||r||_1 <= %6.1e*||b||_1 + %6.1e = %6.1e\n", tol_w,tol,nrm2);
730  }
731  break;
732  }
733  if( A->my_rank==0 )
734  {
735  if( AA->matrix_type==LIS_MATRIX_BSR || AA->matrix_type==LIS_MATRIX_BSC )
736  {
737 #ifdef _LONGLONG
738  if( output ) printf("storage : %s(%lld x %lld)\n", lis_storagename[AA->matrix_type-1],block,block);
739 #else
740  if( output ) printf("storage : %s(%d x %d)\n", lis_storagename[AA->matrix_type-1],block,block);
741 #endif
742  }
743  else
744  {
745  if( output ) printf("storage : %s\n", lis_storagename[AA->matrix_type-1]);
746  }
747  }
748 
749 
750  /* create work vector */
751  err = lis_solver_malloc_work[nsolver](solver);
752  if( err )
753  {
754  lis_vector_destroy(xx);
755  lis_precon_destroy(precon);
756  solver->retcode = err;
757  return err;
758  }
759  if( nsolver==LIS_SOLVER_BICG && is_use_at )
760  {
761  if( output ) lis_printf(A->comm,"Use At\n");
762  lis_matrix_duplicate(AA,&At);
763  lis_matrix_set_type(At,LIS_USE_AT_TYPE[AA->matrix_type]);
764  lis_matrix_convert(AA,At);
765  solver->At = At;
766  }
767 
768  solver->x = xx;
769  solver->xx = x;
770  solver->precon = precon;
771  solver->residual = residual;
772 
773  /* execute solver */
774  #ifndef USE_QUAD_PRECISION
775  err = lis_solver_execute[nsolver](solver);
776  #else
777  if( precision==LIS_PRECISION_DOUBLE )
778  {
779  err = lis_solver_execute[nsolver](solver);
780  }
781  else if( precision==LIS_PRECISION_QUAD )
782  {
783  err = lis_solver_execute_quad[nsolver](solver);
784  }
785  else if( precision==LIS_PRECISION_SWITCH )
786  {
787  err = lis_solver_execute_switch[nsolver](solver);
788  }
789  #endif
790  solver->retcode = err;
791 
792  if( scale==LIS_SCALE_SYMM_DIAG && precon_type!=LIS_PRECON_TYPE_IS)
793  {
794  #ifdef _OPENMP
795  #pragma omp parallel for
796  #endif
797  for(i=0;i<n;i++)
798  {
799  x->value[i] = xx->value[i]*solver->d->value[i];
800  }
801  }
802  else
803  {
804  #ifndef USE_QUAD_PRECISION
805  lis_vector_copy(xx,x);
806  #else
807  if( precision==LIS_PRECISION_DOUBLE )
808  {
809  lis_vector_copy(xx,x);
810  }
811  else
812  {
813  lis_vector_copyex_mn(xx,x);
814  }
815  #endif
816  }
817  itimes = lis_wtime() - itimes - solver->ptimes;
818  p_i_times = solver->ptimes;
819  solver->ptimes = p_c_times + p_i_times;
820  solver->p_c_times = p_c_times;
821  solver->p_i_times = p_i_times;
822  solver->times = solver->ptimes + itimes;
823  solver->itimes = itimes;
824  lis_solver_work_destroy(solver);
825  lis_vector_duplicate(A,&t);
826  xx->precision = LIS_PRECISION_DEFAULT;
827  lis_matvec(A,xx,t);
828  lis_vector_xpay(b,-1.0,t);
829  if( scale==LIS_SCALE_SYMM_DIAG && precon_type!=LIS_PRECON_TYPE_IS)
830  {
831  #ifdef _OPENMP
832  #pragma omp parallel for
833  #endif
834  for(i=0;i<n;i++)
835  {
836  t->value[i] = t->value[i]/solver->d->value[i];
837  }
838  }
839  lis_vector_nrm2(t,&nrm2);
840  /*
841  solver->resid = nrm2;
842  */
843  if( A->my_rank==0 )
844  {
845  if( err )
846  {
847 #ifdef _LONGLONG
848  if( output ) printf("lis_solve : %s(code=%lld)\n\n",lis_returncode[err],err);
849 #else
850  if( output ) printf("lis_solve : %s(code=%d)\n\n",lis_returncode[err],err);
851 #endif
852  }
853  else
854  {
855  if( output ) printf("lis_solve : normal end\n\n");
856  }
857  }
858  if( precision==LIS_PRECISION_DOUBLE )
859  {
860  solver->iter2 = solver->iter;
861  }
862  else if( precision==LIS_PRECISION_QUAD )
863  {
864  solver->iter2 = 0;
865  }
866 
867 
868  lis_vector_destroy(t);
869 /* lis_vector_destroy(d);*/
870  lis_vector_destroy(xx);
871 
872  LIS_DEBUG_FUNC_OUT;
873  return LIS_SUCCESS;
874 }
